In this blog post I want to cover all the concepts behind transformers. As my main research topic as of right now, my main idea is to recycle what I write here for my thesis. For that reason, in every section there is a "show detailed explanation" button that changes the text in a more academic manner.

There are lots of blog posts explaining transformers out there on the internet. My intention is to explain the topic as a researcher from a more technical point of view, focusing on implementations details, matrix shapes, equations, paper references...

